INSERT INTO `wp_rg_lead_detail_long` VALUES('3227', 'Hi,\r\n\r\nI came across Sterling Wellness Solutions while searching for organizations to reach out to about mesothelioma awareness. The educational research, resources, and information that you are providing is honestly quite remarkable. I found the workplace health facts to be really interesting. I liked how you compared food prices to medical inflation – such a great visual and approach!  \r\n\r\nI contacted you because I’m part of the Community Outreach team at Mesothelioma Guide. We are a new site reaching out to provide up-to-date support to mesothelioma patients and family members. Mesothelioma is a rare cancer, only affecting 2,000 – 3,000 patients a year. Although this number may be small relative to other cancerous diseases, it is almost always 100% fatal. Any individual or family that is diagnosed with or knows someone with cancer deserves to have the best information and support available. Our goal at Mesothelioma Guide is to increase mesothelioma awareness.\r\n\r\nI noticed you have a link for health related resources, here – http://www.sterling-wellness.com/resources/. I think our site would be a great addition and benefit to your users. Do you mind including our link as well? \r\n\r\nBest,\r\n\r\nShelby Gehrdes Community Outreach\r\nMesothelioma Guide: 1-888-983-0667\r\n121 S. Orange Avenue | Suite 1450 | Orlando, FL 32801\r\nhttp://www.MesotheliomaGuide.com\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n');
