INSERT INTO `wp_rg_lead_detail_long` VALUES('3384', 'Hi there,\r\n\r\nMy name is Laura and I am writing as a mother of two lovely daughters because recently I was shocked by how little they knew about STD risks. Part of this has been my own failure as a parent, but also a lack of quality education and awareness.\r\n\r\nIn the United States, the MAC AIDS Fund has done some research into STD awareness among teenagers and has found that awareness levels are worryingly low. For example, only 59% of sexually active teenagers have been using condoms while 40% of new HIV infections are in people aged 15 to 24.\r\n\r\nWith this in mind, I thought I would use my position as a health writer to put together a small article on HIV risk in particular - http://www.kwikmed.org/american-teens-unaware-hiv-risks/\r\n\r\nI would love for this to be listed as a resource on your site or for you to use it in a discussion of the subject. Alternatively, I am very happy to write a piece for your site on STD awareness or HIV awareness if you want. Just let me know your thoughts.\r\n\r\nBest Regards,\r\nLaura');
