INSERT INTO `wp_rg_lead_detail_long` VALUES('3868', 'Hi,\r\n\r\nI came across Sterling Wellness Solutions while searching for organizations to reach out to about mesothelioma awareness. Your team’s dedication to delivering comprehensive wellness services to your client partners and their employees to reduce health risk factors and decrease health care expenditures is essential. I understand you are a corporate wellness program provider, but I believe that we are all together in the battle against illnesses and cancers of all kinds.\r\n\r\nI contacted you because I’m part of the Community Outreach team at Mesothelioma Guide. We are a new site reaching out to provide up-to-date support to mesothelioma patients and family members. Mesothelioma is a rare cancer, only affecting 2,000 – 3,000 patients a year. Although this number may be small relative to other cancerous diseases, it is almost always 100% fatal. Any individual or family that is diagnosed with or knows someone with cancer deserves to have the best information and support available. Our goal at Mesothelioma Guide is to increase mesothelioma awareness.\r\n\r\nI noticed you have a link for health and cancer related resources, here– http://www.sterling-wellness.com/resources/. I think our site would be a great addition and benefit to your users. Do you mind including our link as well? \r\n\r\nBest,\r\n\r\nChloe Ryniewicz Community Outreach\r\nMesothelioma Guide:  \r\n121 S. Orange Avenue | Suite 1470 | Orlando, FL 32801\r\nhttp://www.MesotheliomaGuide.com');
